    "18": {
      "id": "18",
      "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
      "text": "What a sight for sore eyes. I believe there's somewhere you're supposed to be, no? Long overdue, in fact.",
      "context": "",
      "checkflags": [
        "COM",
        "SHADOWHEART_SHARPATH"
      ],
      "setflags": [],
      "ruletags": [],
      "approval": [],
      "rolls": "",
      "goto": "",
      "link": "34",
      "is_end": false,
      "node_type": "normal",
      "children": {
        "43": {
          "id": "43",
          "speaker": "Shadowheart",
          "text": "Do I know you?",
          "context": "NodeContext: Overall arc: Shadowheart has been blessed by her goddess Shar after sacrificing Nightsong. She is now on a mission to seize control of Shar's church and followers in Baldur's Gate",
          "checkflags": [],
          "setflags": [],
          "ruletags": [],
          "approval": [],
          "rolls": "",
          "goto": "",
          "link": "34",
          "is_end": false,
          "node_type": "normal",
          "children": {
            "0": {
              "id": "0",
              "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
              "text": "No, but I know you. I was told to keep watch for you and point you towards home, should you ever appear.",
              "context": "",
              "checkflags": [],
              "setflags": [],
              "ruletags": [],
              "approval": [],
              "rolls": "",
              "goto": "",
              "link": "34",
              "is_end": false,
              "node_type": "normal",
              "children": {
                "23": {
                  "id": "23",
                  "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
                  "text": "And lo, you have appeared.",
                  "context": "",
                  "checkflags": [],
                  "setflags": [],
                  "ruletags": [],
                  "approval": [],
                  "rolls": "",
                  "goto": "",
                  "link": "34",
                  "is_end": false,
                  "node_type": "normal",
                  "children": {
                    "45": {
                      "id": "45",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "Who sent you?",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "34",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {}
                    },
                    "33": {
                      "id": "33",
                      "speaker": "Player",
                      "text": "Spit it out, then. Where's she supposed to go?",
                      "context": "",
                      "checkflags": [],
                      "setflags": [],
                      "ruletags": [],
                      "approval": [],
                      "rolls": "",
                      "goto": "",
                      "link": "34",
                      "is_end": false,
                      "node_type": "normal",
                      "children": {
                        "6": {
                          "id": "6",
                          "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
                          "text": "Your friend is inquisitive. A dangerous trait. Are you sure you want them listening in on this?",
                          "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Ferg tosses the player a cold look before returning his attention to Shadowheart, addressing her.",
                          "checkflags": [],
                          "setflags": [],
                          "ruletags": [],
                          "approval": [],
                          "rolls": "",
                          "goto": "",
                          "link": "19",
                          "is_end": false,
                          "node_type": "normal",
                          "children": {
                            "40": {
                              "id": "40",
                              "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                              "text": "Yes, I trust them. Whatever you have to say, say it.",
                              "context": "NodeContext: Overall arc: Shadowheart has been blessed by her goddess Shar after sacrificing Nightsong. She is now on a mission to seize control of Shar's church and followers in Baldur's Gate",
                              "checkflags": [],
                              "setflags": [],
                              "ruletags": [],
                              "approval": [],
                              "rolls": "",
                              "goto": "",
                              "link": "19",
                              "is_end": false,
                              "node_type": "normal",
                              "children": {
                                "5": {
                                  "id": "5",
                                  "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
                                  "text": "Very well. First, you need to continue onwards into the Lower City.",
                                  "context": "CinematicNodeContext: Indifferent shrug on 'very well'\rNodeContext: Indifferent shrug on 'very well' ('it's your head')",
                                  "checkflags": [],
                                  "setflags": [],
                                  "ruletags": [],
                                  "approval": [],
                                  "rolls": "",
                                  "goto": "",
                                  "link": "19",
                                  "is_end": false,
                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                  "children": {
                                    "47": {
                                      "id": "47",
                                      "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
                                      "text": "Then seek out a place called the House of Grief. It may not be quite what you expect, but I assure you it's the right spot. Go there, and make yourself known. You will be given the welcome you deserve.",
                                      "context": "",
                                      "checkflags": [],
                                      "setflags": [
                                        "LOW_HouseOfGrief_Knows_IsSharCult",
                                        "ORI_Shadowheart_Knows_GrottoLocation"
                                      ],
                                      "ruletags": [],
                                      "approval": [],
                                      "rolls": "",
                                      "goto": "",
                                      "link": "19",
                                      "is_end": false,
                                      "node_type": "normal",
                                      "children": {
                                        "8": {
                                          "id": "8",
                                          "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                                          "text": "Can't you show me yourself?",
                                          "context": "NodeContext: Overall arc: Shadowheart has been blessed by her goddess Shar after sacrificing Nightsong. She is now on a mission to seize control of Shar's church and followers in Baldur's Gate",
                                          "checkflags": [],
                                          "setflags": [],
                                          "ruletags": [],
                                          "approval": [],
                                          "rolls": "",
                                          "goto": "",
                                          "link": "19",
                                          "is_end": false,
                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                          "children": {
                                            "26": {
                                              "id": "26",
                                              "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
                                              "text": "Oh no, I must remain here. In truth, I'm glad to keep my distance for now... There's been some tension in the ranks. It seems a great deal is riding on the outcome of your mission.",
                                              "context": "",
                                              "checkflags": [],
                                              "setflags": [
                                                "ORI_Shadowheart_Knows_SharransDivided"
                                              ],
                                              "ruletags": [],
                                              "approval": [],
                                              "rolls": "",
                                              "goto": "",
                                              "link": "19",
                                              "is_end": false,
                                              "node_type": "normal",
                                              "children": {
                                                "12": {
                                                  "id": "12",
                                                  "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
                                                  "text": "Besides, I have business to attend to, wares to sell. Our great endeavour cannot run on faith alone - we need funds. Have a look, if you wish.",
                                                  "context": "",
                                                  "checkflags": [],
                                                  "setflags": [
                                                    "WYR_RefugeeCamp_State_InformerGoodsAvailable"
                                                  ],
                                                  "ruletags": [],
                                                  "approval": [],
                                                  "rolls": "",
                                                  "goto": "",
                                                  "link": "19",
                                                  "is_end": false,
                                                  "node_type": "normal",
                                                  "children": {
                                                    "21": {
                                                      "id": "21",
                                                      "speaker": "",
                                                      "text": "",
                                                      "context": "",
                                                      "checkflags": [
                                                        "ORI_Shadowheart_State_NobleStalkMemory",
                                                        "REALLY_SHADOWHEART"
                                                      ],
                                                      "setflags": [],
                                                      "ruletags": [],
                                                      "approval": [],
                                                      "rolls": "",
                                                      "goto": "",
                                                      "link": "19",
                                                      "is_end": false,
                                                      "node_type": "alias",
                                                      "children": {
                                                        "17": {
                                                          "id": "17",
                                                          "speaker": "Shadowheart",
                                                          "text": "Tell me one thing... Is there someone called Rennald there? A tiefling boy, or possibly a man now.",
                                                          "context": "NodeContext: Referring to a memory fragment she had restored previously, hinting at a childhood friend she can't remember. Overall arc: Shadowheart has been blessed by her goddess Shar after sacrificing Nightsong. She is now on a mission to seize control of Shar's church and followers in Baldur's Gate",
                                                          "checkflags": [],
                                                          "setflags": [],
                                                          "ruletags": [],
                                                          "approval": [],
                                                          "rolls": "",
                                                          "goto": "",
                                                          "link": "",
                                                          "is_end": false,
                                                          "node_type": "normal",
                                                          "children": {
                                                            "32": {
                                                              "id": "32",
                                                              "speaker": "Ferg Drogher",
                                                              "text": "Rennald... Now there's a name I haven't heard in some time. But not for me to spoil what Lady Shar would keep hidden from you. Best if you looked for yourself.",
                                                              "context": "NodeContext: Knowing smile",
                                                              "checkflags": [],
                                                              "setflags": [
                                                                "WYR_RefugeeCamp_State_InformerEndedOM"
